data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":276,"item_id":"msg_a103a408f62cb61c006939d5a143e0819094a86ab9f91ec9d9","output_index":1,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso offers a product line under the \"Contoso Galaxy Innovations\" brand that features Smart Eyewear, specifically their SmartView Glasses. Here are the detailed features of this product:\n\n1. **Augmented Reality Interface**: The SmartView Glasses provide an immersive augmented reality experience, allowing users to interact with digital elements in the real world seamlessly.\n\n2. **Voice-Controlled AI Agent**: A built-in AI agent that responds to voice commands, enabling intuitive hands-free control and assistance.\n\n3. **HD Video Recording with 3D Audio**: These glasses are equipped with HD video recording capabilities combined with 3D audio, offering a rich multimedia experience.\n\n4. **UV Protection and Blue Light Filtering**: Integrated filters offer protection against UV rays and reduce blue light exposure, promoting better eye health during extended use.\n\n5. **Wireless Charging with Extended Battery Life**: Designed for convenience, the SmartView Glasses support wireless charging and feature a long-lasting battery to ensure uninterrupted use.\n\nAdditionally, the product comes with a comprehensive user guide that includes sections on introduction, sizing and fit, proper care and maintenance, safety tips, and troubleshooting. There is also a two-year limited warranty for all electronic components. Information about syncing the glasses with devices and customizing the augmented reality environment is provided in the FAQ section.","logprobs":[]}

